high_descs: Turn right and go to the left side of the toilet.
Pick up the candle on the toilet.
Turn right and go to the shelf on the right.
Put the candle on the shelf.
Turn right and go back to the toilet.
Pick up the candle on the back of the toilet.
Turn right and go back to the shelf.
Put the candle on the shelf to the left of the other candle.
anns.task_desc: Put two candles on the shelf.

turn to face toilet

high_descs: Move around to the other side of the toilet on your left.
Pick up the candle on the left side of the toilet tank lid.
Turn right, bring the candle to the first white shelf on the right, turn right to face the shelf.
Put the candle on the shelf, left of the empty toilet paper tube.
Turn right, go to the wall, turn right to face the left side of the toilet.
Pick up the candle on the toilet tank lid.
Turn right, go to the first white shelf on the right, turn right to face the shelf.
Put the candle on the shelf, left of the other candle.
